Product description

DONUT 22 SPECIAL EDITION REBREATHER I:

- Donut 22 Special Edition designed for CCR rebreather diving

- Customised length of the inflator hose

- 5-year warranty on the bladder and valves

 

SPECIFICATIONS:

- Capacity: 22L

- Double layer wing

- Inner bladder made of durable PU-420

- External layer made of Cordura 1000D

- Two rows of holes for fixing screws

- 5-year warranty on the bladder and valves

- Narrow profile in the top section, extended side and bottom sections

- Personalization possible = name or logo embroidery

 

Attention!

Please contact our representatives to order personalized wing:
